{"tid":2386193,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（捉鬼） 政府：公務員發放不實訊息或指控有損團隊形像","createTime":"2021-01-29T12:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T13:36:46.000Z","uid":230530,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b8b76c0303d32b135c7a540256ea9e9fe3a2dc6c","tid":2386193,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:19:28.000Z","msg":"特區政府上星期在佐敦指定「受限區域」實施強制檢測行動，動員約3000名公務員參與，政府發言人說，若公務員對有關行動的人事編配有疑問，各部門樂意解答問題。但如有同事對外發放不實訊息或指控，除嚴重影響政府在抗疫方面的工作，亦有損公務員團隊的公眾形象，對其他積極參與的同事有欠公允，重申在抗疫工作上，所有政府部門及各級公務員均責無旁貸。 發言人說，相信絕大部分公務員都以公眾利益為大前提，希望發揮一己之力，參與有關行動，好讓香港盡早走出疫情。"},{"pid":"677ee1b6189bc73e6bed0f783ca535dd4f986b29","tid":2386193,"uid":174013,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:20:35.000Z","msg":"放相果個死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定迫老細交人"},{"pid":"ac788ea2e8ba0aedf982bf14958c3e65ec918e16","tid":2386193,"uid":230530,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"677ee1b6189bc73e6bed0f783ca535dd4f986b29","tid":2386193,"uid":174013,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:20:35.000Z","msg":"放相果個死硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定迫老細交人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:22:45.000Z","msg":"個條友應該唔做<br />\n但咁樣比埋記者隨時鋤不誠實使用電腦"},{"pid":"805fb7e276a07a084ed66264dd1ea986c9b62f96","tid":2386193,"uid":214502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:23:00.000Z","msg":"炒左個成撚日有幻聽既特首先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283e26a18a50b82e7ee168edc3d08e3365b26ba7","tid":2386193,"uid":59976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:23:31.000Z","msg":"宣左誓就預左做走狗架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6177cfc020867087e4fd7ba46daf8c64a03ab196","tid":2386193,"uid":379566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:23:47.000Z","msg":"咩事？"},{"pid":"5da58db96eaab5fd8af43fe5a346c6503